I just can't believe Susan has done this to me.

22
00:02:50,820 --> 00:02:52,370
奥布瑞恩小姐确实说过
Miss O'Brien did say that

23
00:02:52,370 --> 00:02:54,760
弗林特夏尔夫人与她在苏格兰时
she got on very well with Lady Flintshire

24
00:02:54,760 --> 00:02:55,950
相处甚欢
when she was up in Scotland.

25
00:02:55,950 --> 00:02:57,540
我想也是
So I gather!

26
00:02:58,090 --> 00:03:01,310
弗林特夏尔夫人已为我订了去印度的车票
"Lady Flintshire has booked my ticket for India

27
00:03:01,310 --> 00:03:04,200
机会难得  错过实在可惜
"And it seems too good a chance to miss."

28
00:03:05,110 --> 00:03:06,810
