Was there really no warning?

29
00:03:06,870 --> 00:03:10,820
现在想来  昨天她接到一通电报
Now I think of it, she'd a telegram yesterday.

30
00:03:10,990 --> 00:03:12,710
一定是为这事
That must have been it.

31
00:03:13,130 --> 00:03:14,810
现在怎么办
So what happens now?

32
00:03:14,930 --> 00:03:17,060
今天由我为您更衣  夫人
I'll dress you today, m'lady,

33
